data.description: This beautiful and spacious home is nestled seven miles from the Beach on a cul-de-sac in the coveted North Hampton's Community with a golf course designed by Arnold Palmer, outpost for fishing and canoeing, community center with an olympic size pool, soccer field, basketball court, tennis and pickle ball courts, fire pits and a playground. HOA fees include all of the above along with internet, cable and security. This 5 Bedroom/3 full bath (1 being a large flex room with 2 closets) has had many updates over the past few years including a new roof, new flooring, remodeled Kitchen with quartz countertops, fresh Paint, and a water softener/filter system. As you enter the home you will be greeted by an inviting open floor plan with living/dining combo, fireplace, a newly remodeled kitchen, s tainless steel appliances and breakfast bar with additional eat in dining area.  Off the kitchen is the laundry room and 2 car garage.  The primary bedroom boasts oversized windows allowing for ample natural light and bath featuring dual vanities, soaking tub, separate shower and large walk-in closet. Also off the living area is 2 bedrooms with a bathroom in the middle and the large flex room.  Upstairs features a bonus room ensuite with full bath.  Possibilities here are endless.. Enjoy sipping on your favorite beverage in your screened in lanai which overlooks the large estate sized backyard.  This home is a must see!!!
